name: Bug Breaker
summary:
Squash, Shoot, Survive!

 Put on the gloves of the galaxy’s most daring Space Exterminator in BUG BREAKER! A thrilling new VR game where only you can save the space station from an intergalactic infestation of alien bugs and bricks!

Your station’s passages are plagued by extraterrestrial brick blockages and alien bug hordes invading the system. It’s up to you to clear the chaos as the hero exterminator the galaxy never knew it needed!
